'''牙粉'''是粉狀的[[潔齒劑|潔齒劑]]，是[[牙膏|牙膏]]的替代品。可分為[[氟化物|氟化物]]跟非氟化物兩類。

== 歷史 ==

在[[古羅馬|古羅馬]]人們常用牙粉作清潔。骨頭、蹄、特定動物的角、螃蟹、蛋殼、牡蠣或海螺殼等在烤過後磨成粉狀，並且有時會添加蜂蜜、[[沒藥|沒藥]]或[[硝石|硝石]]。<ref>{{cite book |last=Smith |first=William |date=1875 |title=A Dictionary of Greek and Roman Antiquities |url=http://penelope.uchicago.edu/Thayer/E/Roman/Texts/secondary/SMIGRA*/Dentifricium.html}} </ref>

[[阿普列尤斯|阿普列尤斯]]寫信曾提到：
<blockquote>
「我寄給你，如你請我作的，為清理牙齒跟燦爛笑容，阿拉比產品，小粉末高尚、優質、美白，能減緩您牙齦腫，刷除昨日的殘渣，讓你開唇大笑時沒有髒東西被看到。」
</blockquote>

在 1924 年，[[矽藻土|矽藻土]]曾被開採來作為原料<ref>{{Cite journal | title = Toothpowder Mountain Built From Shells | journal = Popular Mechanics | date = Feb 1924 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=JtsDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA209&lpg=PA209&dq=tooth+powder+mountain&source=bl&ots=zKQWLwNwm5&sig=IzwSsPLyVBAIABkVWGonYzbnjpw&hl=en&ei=u0oLTMnZHMT48Abmx8HtCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBsQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=tooth%20powder%20mountain&f=false | access-date = 2017-02-23 | archive-date = 2017-02-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170223220754/https://books.google.com/books?id=JtsDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA209&lpg=PA209&dq=tooth+powder+mountain&source=bl&ots=zKQWLwNwm5&sig=IzwSsPLyVBAIABkVWGonYzbnjpw&hl=en&ei=u0oLTMnZHMT48Abmx8HtCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBsQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=tooth%20powder%20mountain&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在現代，[[蘇打粉|蘇打粉]]是最常見的牙粉成份。但是牙粉已經被[[牙膏|牙膏]]所取代。

